metadata.name: Living Legend (You are not) #1/25
metadata.description:
From the poet “You are not the legend”

Living so long like a 🦒
See a sunshine 🌞
I’m not John Lennon
Because iam not saying “The world must be peace”
Don’t say anything, iam not 
🤷🏼‍♂️

Painting about a legend from each other say but he haven’t to become a legend, whatever say from other people and iam not🤷🏼‍♂️
